Write a Java program to calculate the sum of the digit number. It is given that the number is always a 3 digit number.

Input Format
The first line contain n.

Output Format
Print the sum of the digit number.

Example 1
Input

122
Output

5


import java.util.*;

public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();  // input 3-digit number
        
        int sum = 0;
        
        while (n > 0) {
            int digit = n % 10;   // get last digit
            sum += digit;         // add to sum
            n = n / 10;           // remove last digit
        }
        
        System.out.println(sum);
    }
}
